`` Before the railway returned I only had part-time work and could n't send my children to school , '' she says . `` Since the trains returned life is much better . ''

Avenue of the Volcanoes is highlight

The journey to Quito passes 10 volcanoes along the so-called Avenue of Volcanoes .

